article_title: 22 killed in Israeli strike, Gaza Civil Defence says.
sentence: At  least  22  people  are  reported  to  have  been  killed  and  dozens  wounded  in  an  Israeli  air  strike  on  a  school  building  in  northern  Gaza,  according  to  Gaza's  Hamas-run  Civil  Defence  Agency.
